@startuml seq_22_report_violation
title Sequence Diagram: UC-22 Report Violation

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Report Controller" as Controller
participant "Report Service" as Service
participant "Report Repo" as Repo
participant "Target Repo" as TargetRepo

User -> Frontend: Fill report form & Submit
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/reports {target_id, type, reason}
Controller -> Service: Create Report
Service -> TargetRepo: Validate target exists (Post/Comment/Community)
TargetRepo --> Service: Target is valid

Service -> Repo: Create Report record (Status: Pending)
Repo --> Service: Report created
Service --> Controller: Success
Controller --> Frontend: 201 Created
Frontend --> User: Show "Report submitted" message
@enduml